propClasses: Override or extend the styles applied to the component.
propColor: The dot can have a different colors.
propVariant: The dot can appear filled or outlined.
stylesRoot: Styles applied to the root element.
stylesFilled: Styles applied to the root element if `variant="filled"`.
stylesOutlined: Styles applied to the root element if `variant="outlined"`.
stylesFilledGrey: Styles applied to the root element if `color="grey"` and `variant="filled"`.
stylesOutlinedGrey: Styles applied to the root element if `color="grey"` and `variant="outlined"`.
stylesFilledPrimary: Styles applied to the root element if `color="primary"` and `variant="filled"`.
stylesOutlinedPrimary: Styles applied to the root element if `color="primary"` and `variant="outlined"`.
stylesFilledSecondary: Styles applied to the root element if `color="secondary"` and `variant="filled"`.
stylesOutlinedSecondary: Styles applied to the root element if `color="secondary"` and `variant="outlined"`.
